### What this PR does

The PR increases the Railway token health check from weekly (`0 9 * * 1` — Mondays only) to daily (`0 9 * * *`). This reduces the worst-case time to detect token expiry from ~6 days to ~23 hours, preventing recurring deploy failures like #755, #742, #739, and #733.

### Next steps

The PR includes:
- ✅ Code change: daily health check cron schedule
- ✅ Validation: all tests pass, TypeScript clean, no lint errors
- ✅ Issue linkage: references `Part of #755`

